entries.femaleVariant: Fuck, I dunno 'bout you all, but I'ma dig my own chrome out myself.
Wait, what? You need the eds or somethin'?
Nah, I just don't need them scavs. They already grabbed five on my street. Just come in at night, drag 'em out to the van... and that's it, gone without a trace.
What, think if you ain't got implants, they'll leave you be?
Ain't like they ask what you packin' first. They just slice 'n' dice. So keep your chrome, and get you some iron, too.
